---
title: Cajun Chicken Salad with Feta and Lentils
description: We’re un-Cajun the beast - of flavour that is! Let your imagination and your senses run wild with a delicious spice rub with a hint of spice. To keep it tame, we’ve paired it with some cool and fresh cucumber.
